# Project Context — RFE

## Identity
- **RFE** (Rohm Feifer Entertainment) — a woman-owned film & TV production company
- This is a **content-driven showcase website**, not a backend service
- The codebase is being **progressively migrated** from a hardcoded Next.js site to an integrated **Next.js + Payload CMS** application

## Stack
- **Runtime:** Next.js 16 + React 19
- **Package manager:** pnpm
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS v4 (via `@tailwindcss/postcss`, no `tailwind.config` file)
- **CMS:** Payload CMS (integrated — runs in the same Next.js app)
- **Database:** PostgreSQL
- **Object storage:** S3-compatible (MinIO locally, S3/R2 in production)
- **Fonts:** Sackers Gothic (brand), Inter, Fraunces (Google Fonts)
- **i18n:** `[locale]` segment routing, currently `en` + `fr`

## Key file locations
| Concern | Path |
|---------|------|
| App routes | `app/[locale]/` |
| Locale middleware | `middleware.ts` |
| Components | `components/` |
| Design tokens / CSS | `app/[locale]/globals.css` |
| Content data (hardcoded) | `app/[locale]/content.ts` |
| i18n fallback strings | `lib/i18n/fallback/en.ts`, `fr.ts` |
| i18n types | `lib/i18n/types.ts` |
| SEO config | `lib/seo.ts` |
| Work item helpers | `lib/works.ts` |
| Static assets | `public/assets/` |
| Logos | `public/assets/logos/`, `public/logo-rfe*.svg`, `public/favicon.png` |
| Poster images | `public/assets/works/`, `public/assets/posters/` |
| Team photos | `public/assets/team/` |
| Brand font | `public/fonts/sackers-gothic.woff2` |

## Payload CMS target structure (when introduced)
| Concern | Expected path |
|---------|---------------|
| Payload config | `payload.config.ts` |
| Collections | `collections/` |
| Globals | `globals/` |
| Blocks | `blocks/` |
| Seed scripts | `scripts/seed/` or `src/seed/` |
| Payload route group | `app/(payload)/` |
| Frontend route group | `app/(frontend)/[locale]/` |

## Design system summary
The current branding lives in CSS variables in `app/[locale]/globals.css`:
- **Background:** `#070708` (near-black)
- **Foreground:** `#F5F0EB` (warm off-white)
- **RFE Red:** `#8B1A1A`
- **RFE Rose:** `#C4A0A0`
- **RFE Gold:** `#B5975A`
- **Section tones:** deep, charcoal, slate, warm, cool, ember, dusk (near-black variants)
- **Easings:** emerge (expo out), quiet (slow in/out), sharp (decisive)
- **Radius:** 0.25rem base
- **Font stack:** Sackers Gothic → Inter → system-ui

## Conventions
- Use TypeScript for all new code
- Use `@/` path alias (maps to repo root)
- Prefer server components; use `'use client'` only when needed
- Mobile-first responsive design (Tailwind responsive classes)
- Minimum touch targets: 44×44px
- Semantic HTML, ARIA labels, accessible components
- No `eslint` config currently committed (add if needed)
